<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Welcome to Battles Birds game!</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="main">
            <div class="content animation-appear wrong-zone">
                <h1>You are banned. You was a bad boy (girl).</h1>
                <p> You banned to: 
                  <%= 
                  ( (
                     time.getHours() < 10 
                      ? '0'+ time.getHours() 
                      : time.getHours()
                     ) + 
                    ':' + (
                            time.getMinutes() < 10 
                              ? '0' + time.getMinutes() 
                              : time.getMinutes()
                          ) + 
                    ' ' + (
                            time.getDate() < 10 
                              ? '0' + time.getDate() 
                              : time.getDate()
                          ) + 
                    '-' + ( time.getMonth() < 9 
                            ? '0' + (1 + time.getMonth())
                            : (1 + time.getMonth())
                          ) 
                    + '-' + time.getFullYear() )
                  %></p>
                <p>I hope you will change your behavior in future.</p>
                <p>And now, let see this amazing kitten!</p>
                <img src="images/kitten.jpg" style="margin:50px auto;width:100%" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>